name: VNBarcodeObservation
desc: An object that represents barcode information that an image analysis request detects.

items.name: var payloadStringValue: String?
items.desc: A string value that represents the barcode payload.

items.name: var barcodeDescriptor: CIBarcodeDescriptor?
items.desc: An object that describes the low-level details about the barcode and its data.

items.name: var symbology: VNBarcodeSymbology
items.desc: The symbology of the observed barcode.
